            <lg xml:id="TK41">
<l>ilvāḻvā ṉeṉpā ṉiyalpuṭaiya mūvarkku</l>
<l>nallāṟṟi ṉiṉṟa tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will be called a (true) householder, who is a firm support to the virtuous of the three orders in their good path.</l>
            </lg>
